  "secondName": "Mercurial Mastermind",
  "description": "The Devil. Fifteenth Arcana of the Tarot. The card of duplicity, corruption, and inescapable fate.\n\nCyrus learned to read the cards as a boy, the poor bastard of a lord. Even as a child, he was no fool; his use to his father would end the moment his wife bore him a true heir. Rather than wait to be unceremoniously murdered, he ran away and joined an underground ring of thieves masquerading as soothsayers and fortune tellers. His skill with a deck served him well, but unlike his comrades, Cyrus told no lies.\n\nThe misfortunes he predicted had a way of coming true.",
